{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"PERF NOTE (follow-up, not blocking): the correctness fix is confirmed (0 kmva) but adding --full-history to resolve_event_commit/resolve_position_commit made the era-check hot path (verify_authorship_at_commit -> resolve_event_commit per key per event) scan more history, so the whole-store gate got slower (780's CI verify-identity job ~66min vs ~57min before; local enforcement run >35min). build_position_commit_map only batches the ledger NULL re-resolution, not the per-key era resolution. Follow-up optimization: batch verify_authorship_at_commit's per-key position->commit lookups through the same one-pass --full-history map instead of per-key git log. Filing as discovered work."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784349385129342001,"uuid":"6d8847a8-eba8-41a3-9e1f-9c0f74b4e590"}